<section class="w-full flex flex-col items-center py-12 px-8 border-b border-black text-center">
  <!-- Starburst Title Approximation -->
  <div class="relative inline-block mb-8">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-transparent border-[3px] border-[#26498d] transform rotate-1 scale-[1.1] z-0" style="clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 61% 35%, 98% 35%, 68% 57%, 79% 91%, 50% 70%, 21% 91%, 32% 57%, 2% 35%, 39% 35%);"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 px-12 py-8 bg-transparent">
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-[#26498d] transform -rotate-3 leading-tight">
        OUR<br/>SERVICES
      </h2>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <p class="font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-4xl text-center mb-12">
    In the interest of public clarity, we hereby present the list of things we do—deliberately, consistently, and with only a reasonable amount of chaos. At Indiefluence, services aren't tossed into the air like confetti; they are constructed with thought, tested with suspicion, and delivered with an enthusiasm that alarms our caffeine suppliers. What follows is not a menu of tasks, but the work we stand by.
  </p>
  
  <div class="w-full flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between">
    <!-- Left text -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-start text-left space-y-8 pr-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-sans font-black text-xl mb-2">Social Media Marketing</h3>
        <p class="font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed">
          We carry your voice across distant platforms, crafting messages that summon attention and strengthen allegiance
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-sans font-black text-xl mb-2">Brand Management</h3>
        <p class="font-serif text-sm leading-relaxed">
          We govern your mark with steady counsel, ensuring all expressions uphold its honour, purpose, and rightful place.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Right illustration -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 mt-8 md:mt-0 flex justify-center">
      <img src="/assets/waKkNXzOtzzRh9ERU0aMOs1Hkhc.png" alt="Hand carrying logos" class="max-h-[400px] object-contain mix-blend-multiply" />
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <a href="#services" class="mt-8 border border-black px-6 py-2 text-[10px] font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition w-full max-w-3xl text-center">
    Browse the Full Ledger
  </a>
</section>
